  <title>VIGRA-&vigra-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      Vision with Generic Algorithms (VIGRA) is a computer vision library that
      puts its main emphasis on customizable algorithms and data structures.
    </para>

